# Salesforce Opportunity Risk Assessment Automation

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates a Salesforce Flow-based automation solution for identifying high-risk sales opportunities.

## Business Problem

Organizations often review high-discount deals manually, which can be time-consuming and inconsistent.

## Solution

A Record-Triggered Flow automatically evaluates Opportunity Discount Percentage.

Business Rule:

- Discount > 20%
    - AI Risk Score = High
    - Approval Required = True

## Salesforce Components Used

- Opportunity Object
- Custom Fields
- Record Triggered Flow
- Flow Decision Element
- Update Records Element

## Custom Fields

- Discount %
- AI Risk Score
- Approval Required
- AI Summary
- AI Recommendation

## Flow Logic

Opportunity Updated
    ↓
Check Discount Risk
    ↓
Discount > 20%
    ↓
Set Risk Score = High
    ↓
Set Approval Required = True

## Business Benefits

- Reduced manual review effort
- Improved sales governance
- Faster approval process
- Consistent risk assessment

